  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h3><strong>Enter our competition for the chance to win a 3 or 4 night Santa Break holiday for 2 adults and 2 children (Family Room) in the <a data-udi="umb://document/85dc830362e2481eb01ef0c39038af6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/85dc830362e2481eb01ef0c39038af6a}" title="Levi Hotel Spa">Levi Hotel Spa</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9dee14339770490983c23ccc11530d35}" title="Santa Breaks in Levi">Levi</a>, Lapland on a half board basis, including flights and transfers.</strong></h3>
<p><strong>Please note the competition opens on 17th November 2022. </strong></p>
<?UMBRACO_MACRO macroAlias="Typeform" WidgetId="h53yBUpQ" Height="730px" />
<p><strong>Highlights of the Levi Hotel Spa</strong></p>
<p><strong><span style="font-weight: 400;">Levi Hotel Spa is Levi's flagship property in a peaceful yet convenient location, just minutes from the ski lifts and village centre. The hotel combines contemporary Finnish design with an exquisite spa experience, combining a high standard of accommodation with an abundance of Nordic-inspired luxury.</span></strong></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/85dc830362e2481eb01ef0c39038af6a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/85dc830362e2481eb01ef0c39038af6a}" title="Levi Hotel Spa"><strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13052597/levi-hotel-spa-levitunturi-exterior.jpg?width=500&amp;height=209.30232558139537" alt="levi hotel spa" data-udi="umb://media/138c31bc886a4d749a1997bf1ff00e95"></span></strong></a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2>RHS Glow Show at Wisley</h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">We're delighted to have been a part of RHS Glow Show at Wisley this year and hope you enjoyed your visit to our cosy cabin and photo-op archway. </span>We can’t wait to see which of the amazing photos you took made it onto our Facebook page, or were featured on Instagram.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Thank you to all our visitors this year. Hopefully, you managed to have a look at our glow show across the lawns, giving you an opportunity to see the wonders of the Northern Lights. </span>Join us, via our competition or by booking <a data-udi="umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f83de191792e4f76a2b62b60cd414e3a}" title="Santa Breaks">Santa Breaks</a> to experience all that Lapland has to offer - be it Husky Rides, Snowmobile Safaris, or a private meeting with Santa himself.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Travelling to Lapland will leave you with memories that will last a lifetime. Witness natural beauty at its very best, from snow-packed forests to frozen lakes. Gaze up at the stunning Northern Lights or enjoy the company of reindeer on this once-in-a-lifetime trip.</span></p>
<h3>Make your own Christmas tree decoration</h3>
<p>Try your hand at Origami by making your own tree Christmas Tree or Santa decoration this Winter, a fun activity to enjoy with family. Simply download and print the instructions below. </p>
