<h2>Terms &amp; Conditions</h2>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;">
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">There is no entry fee and no purchase necessary to enter this competition. </span>Multiple entries from the same person will not qualify. Closing date for entry will be at 21:00 on Sunday 8th January 2023. After this date no further entries to the competition will be permitted. Route to entry for the competition is at RHS Glow, Wisley.</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>The rules of the competition and how to enter are as follows:</strong> To enter, entrants must complete all compulsory sections of the competition entry form. Entry is possible by scanning the QR code on your own mobile device. All sections of the competition form must be completed.</span></p>
<p><strong>The prize includes:</strong><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 3 or 4 night Santa Break holiday for 2 adults and 2 children (Family Room) in the Levi Hotel Spa, Levi, Lapland on a half board basis, including flights and transfers. Supplements for some flights/airports may apply. Date restrictions apply – Holiday must be taken between 26 Nov – 20 Dec 23 (excludes last Santa Break arrival). Dates are subject to availability. The competition prize is not transferable. Prizes are subject to availability and we reserve the right to substitute any prize with another of equivalent value without giving notice.</span></p>
<p><strong>The Prize Draw will take place on WC 9th January 2023 and the winner will be contacted by email shortly afterwards.</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">See full terms and conditions <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/e8cd19288ec342f58c245dff8df5e778" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e8cd19288ec342f58c245dff8df5e778}" title="RHS Glow Show Santa Breaks" data-anchor="#">here.</a> </strong></span></p>
